      Coordinate​(java.lang.String coOrdinate)
      This constructor takes a coordinate in the ALRS formats i.e 38∞31.64'N for lat, and 28∞19.12'W for long Note: ALRS positions are occasionally written with the decimal minutes apostrophe in the 'wrong' place and with a non CP1252 compliant decimal character.
